 Bug Title: High to Low sort does not work

Description: The functionality of sorting the products from price range high to low does not qork, it gets stuck on "Loading"

The steps required to reproduce: Select a category of clothes, Women's dresses in this case. Use the 'sort by' drop down menu to sort 
the displayed items in High to low range of price.

Environment: Google Chrome

Expected results: Display of items in high to low price range.

Assigned to: Vedang Kolhatkar

Severity: Minor
